  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-545'. It calculates the average cycle time from receiving an invoice to approving an invoice for each quarter. The 'Quarter' column is derived by truncating the 'END_TIME' column to the quarter. The 'Avg. Cycle Time (Receive Invoice to Approve Invoice)' column is calculated by subtracting the first 'END_TIME' where the 'EVENT_NAME' is 'Receive invoice' from the last 'END_TIME' where the 'EVENT_NAME' is 'Approve Invoice'. The 'PO Item Line Type' column is also included in the result."
}
